@imesh I've fixed the error where the status of the Member object in the topology is not being properly serialized. member.status is now set to the latest of the status stack from MemberStateManager. The other changes to the Member class in the messaging component was also reflected in the Member class in the Python code. Additionally I've added a unit test to verify serialization of the CompleteTopologyEvent and refactored old unit tests to re enable unit testing for Python agent.
